judgment.error: Order not uploaded by concerned court

business_details.Business: Accused is absent. It is observed that the case is initially registered under section 363/366 of the IPC . The charge sheet was submitted was submitted before the court on 30/05/2019 under section 366 of the IPC with section 8 of the POCSO Act. Inadvertently this court had taken cognizance and issued summons to the accused in spite of the fact that the cases under POCSO Act are exclusively triable by the Hon&amp#039ble Special Judge, Tinsukia. I, therefore, deem it proper to forward the case to the court of the Hon&amp#039ble Special Judge Tinsukia immediately as and when it came to my notice. Send the case record and case diary along with all other relevant materials related to the case to the Hon&amp#039ble court of Special Judge immediately.
